"Scatterblaster is the victor!" the announcer said over the intercom.

The crowd began to leave, not paying attention to Scatterblaster as he 
cheered wildly at his own victory, jumping and doing the splits and getting 
up again.

Several soldiers approached Scatterblaster as a maintenace team began 
cleaning up Wespah, and the guards escorted Scatterblaster to a repair 
chamber.
